# lootTable formatting
# inventory.item: weight
# Weight - higher = more frequent.
# Random loot is generated by grabbing random number skewed towards highest number in weight pool.
# Items with weights above generated number are added to an array,
# after which each loot slot randomly picks from the list with equal chances

